channel.title: Can't get private server online
channel.description:
Hello. I've been trying to get my server to work. Heres what I have done: •DL'd No-Ip DUC •Got a No-Ip address (Pianouxscape.no-ip.org) •Portforwarded 43594 - 43594 to both proto's. •Changed exceptions for that port in my firewall settings •Got a Pimpscape Server source •Got JDK 6u1,2, and 3 •Ran compile.bat
after i did all of that, it still wasn't working.
Please help!

item.title: Can't get private server online
item.dc:creator: @Syrillia Syrillia
item.description:
@Syrillia wrote:

If your portfowarding on 43594, how is someone going to connect to a server on 5555? Your using Pimpscape right? Open server.java and search ‘5555’. Then change it to 43594. Hope it works.
